ayer","jurisdictionLevel":0},{"id":1705202,"age":53,"year":"1558","julianDay":2290108,"title":"Act of Uniformity","description":"The Act of Uniformity was passed by the Parliament of England and required all people to go to church once a week. The consequence of not attending church was a fine of 12 pence, which was a considerable amount for a poor person.","jurisdictionLevel":0},{"id":1705205,"age":64,"year":"1569","julianDay":2294126,"title":"State Lottery","description":"A State Lottery was recorded in 1569. The tickets were sold at St. Paul's Cathedral in London.","jurisdictionLevel":0}],"lifeSummary":"Lockard was born in 1505, in England. He had at least 1 daughter with Lockard."},"et":{"1505–":"1505–Surnud","1505–Female":"1505–Surnud","1525–Female":"1525–Surnud","1505–Male":"1505–Surnud","1525":"1525","1569":"1569","1558":"1558","1505":"1505","1549":"1549","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1505–":"1505–Kuollut","1505–Female":"1505–Kuollut","1525–Female":"1525–Kuollut","1505–Male":"1505–Kuollut","1525":"1525","1569":"1569","1558":"1558","1505":"1505","1549":"1549","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1505–":"1505–Décédé","1505–Female":"1505–Décédée","1525–Female":"1525–Décédée","1505–Male":"1505–Décédé","1525":"1525","1569":"1569","1558":"1558","1505":"1505","1549":"1549","England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lockard est né en 1505, à Angleterre. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Lockard."},"de":{"1505–":"1505–Verstorben","1505–Female":"1505–Verstorben","1525–Female":"1525–Verstorben","1505–Male":"1505–Verstorben","1525":"1525","1569":"1569","1558":"1558","1505":"1505","1549":"1549","England":"England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Lockard wurde 1505 in England geboren. Er hatte mit Lockard mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"1505–":"1505–Desede","1505–Female":"1505–Desede","1525–Female":"1525–Desede","1505–Male":"1505–Desede","1525":"1525","1569":"1569","1558":"1558","1505":"1505","1549":"1549","England":"Angletè, United King